<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>On many AP examinations, scores of 4 or better will earn academic credit; in few cases, score of 3 may result in credit. To receive credit for AP exams, exams and scores must appear on official high school transcript or submit official AP Score Sheet to Registrar's office.</i>
